imdb.title: Muteki kanban musume
imdb.plot: The comical adventures of a ramen delivery girl who loves fighting so much she screws up her job.

episodes.title: Chôsensha Nishiyama Kankurô/Waga tatakai ni shûten nashi
episodes.plot: Kankuro, an old rival of Miki, returns to get his revenge on her.

episodes.title: Katsutenai kyôteki/Anoko no namida wo nuguitai
episodes.plot: Miki and Megumi spar with the fearsome guard dog Toshiyuki.

episodes.title: Tabidachi no mae ni/Watashi ga anata wo michibikimashô
episodes.plot: Miki helps the fearsome teacher Tomoka Kayahara with her self-consciousness problem, and they persuade a delinquent to return to school.

episodes.title: Shiro kuro tsukeyôze/Fumidai wa omae da!
episodes.plot: Three fights take place over different things: a battle over a plush toy, a battle of facial sumo, and finally when everyone is stuck in an alley they fight to see who will have to make a ramp for someone to escape.

episodes.title: Taiketsu! Wan wan vs Nyâ nyâ/Akai ito ni mita mizo
episodes.plot: Kankuro tries to fight Toshiyuki in order to train against Miki.

episodes.title: Hikihagase itsuwari no egao/Sennyû! Oni no su
episodes.plot: Miki attempts to expose Megumi's dark side to everyone.

episodes.title: Tashika ni yatsu wa saikyô ni mieta/Warumono ga yatte kita
episodes.plot: Everyone gets involved in a Power Rangers story.

episodes.title: Ochikaketa kyosei/Kangaeru haha
episodes.plot: Everyone tries to find out Makiko's weakness. Meanwhile, Makiko tries being kinder and nicer to Miki, which upsets her.

episodes.title: Hataraite kachi tore/Gekitotsu! Nishiyama Kankurô vs Kannazuki Megumi
episodes.plot: Kankuro works hard at the ramen shop while Miki makes deliveries, then the two have a short competition to see who's the best poster girl, then later Kankuro and Megimi make an alliance to beat Miki.

episodes.title: Senaka de kataru aitsu/Kishoku manmen shitô
episodes.plot: A Delivery Girl contest pits Miki and Megumi to compete against each other, as well as other female competitors.

episodes.title: Kimi ga kowareta toki/Hômurareta utage
episodes.plot: Miki and Megumi get drunk, and suffer personality changes.
